    <chapter xml:id="basics-of-functions">
      <title>Basics of Functions</title>
      <introduction>
        <p>
          There are four learning outcomes for this unit:
          <ul>
            <li><p>Linear and Quadratic Equations</p></li>
            <li><p>Forms of Linear Equations</p></li>
            <li><p>The Difference Quotient and Piecewise Functions</p></li>
            <li><p>Transformations and Combinations of Functions</p></li>
          </ul> 
        </p>
      </introduction>
      <section xml:id="bf1">
        <title>BF-1 Linear and Quadratic Equations</title>
